sqoop import \
--options-file ./connection.props \
--target-dir /user/bbastola/sqoop_import/customers \
--query 'select customer_id from customers where (customer_id >=300 and customer_id < 901) AND $CONDITIONS' \
--split-by customer_id

when using free form --query
1. no --table argument needed
2. "AND $CONDITIONS" argument needed at the end of the query
3. --split-by argument needed if importing in paralell i.e. using more than 1 mapper
4. else specify --num-mappers 1

